      <aside class="consulting-panel" aria-label="Pilot planning preview">
        <div class="panel-top">
          <p class="panel-label">Guiding principle</p>
          <p class="panel-title">Make the team stronger without taking the wheel away from them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="signal-list">
          <div class="signal-item">
            <span class="signal-num">01</span>
            <span>
              <strong>Find the weight</strong>
              Look for the task that costs the most time, causes the most rework, or keeps skilled people stuck in admin.
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="signal-item">
            <span class="signal-num">02</span>
            <span>
              <strong>Choose the right assist</strong>
              AI might draft, sort, summarize, compare, check, route, remind, search, or prepare the next step.
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="signal-item">
            <span class="signal-num">03</span>
            <span>
              <strong>Keep people in charge</strong>
